1
00:00:06,140 --> 00:00:08,540
=Fireworks=

2
00:00:08,540 --> 00:00:10,860
=Episode 21=

3
00:00:11,375 --> 00:00:12,679
Where did Qiao Nian go?

4
00:00:12,720 --> 00:00:14,800
Where is Qiao Nian? Where is she?

5
00:00:15,240 --> 00:00:16,480
Mr. Jiang, something's wrong.

6
00:00:17,039 --> 00:00:17,839
What is it?

7
00:00:18,039 --> 00:00:19,160
The secret room was opened.

8
00:00:19,719 --> 00:00:20,920
And Ms. Xie is gone.

9
00:00:21,600 --> 00:00:22,600
What?

10
00:00:25,440 --> 00:00:27,000
Qiao Nian pulled it off.

11
00:00:29,960 --> 00:00:32,399
You set me up.

12
00:00:36,240 --> 00:00:37,640
Congratulations on your reunion

13
00:00:37,719 --> 00:00:38,700
and on getting home safe.

14
00:00:39,280 --> 00:00:40,240
Thank you.

15
00:00:40,600 --> 00:00:41,590
We appreciate your help.

16
00:00:41,880 --> 00:00:42,719
Just doing our job.

17
00:00:44,880 --> 00:00:46,600
Get some rest, Ms. Xie.

18
00:00:47,000 --> 00:00:47,920
Okay.

19
00:00:48,840 --> 00:00:50,679
Wen Li and I will be right outside.

20
00:00:50,719 --> 00:00:52,679
Let us know if anything happens.

21
00:00:53,039 --> 00:00:53,840
Got it.

22
00:00:58,439 --> 00:00:59,359
Nian, come here.

23
00:01:04,799 --> 00:01:05,599
Have a seat.

24
00:01:10,519 --> 00:01:12,159
(This place looks exactly the same.)

25
00:01:18,599 --> 00:01:19,359
Mom.

26
00:01:26,480 --> 00:01:27,280
Nian,

27
00:01:32,200 --> 00:01:34,120
all these years I've been gone,

28
00:01:36,120 --> 00:01:37,640
you've grown up so much.

29
00:01:38,319 --> 00:01:39,120
Mom,

30
00:01:42,200 --> 00:01:43,280
what did Jiang Xiao

31
00:01:44,920 --> 00:01:46,920
do to you all these years?

32
00:01:50,480 --> 00:01:51,359
I'm fine.

33
00:01:53,120 --> 00:01:55,200
What did you have to go through for me?

34
00:01:57,760 --> 00:01:59,640
I just regret it so much.

35
00:02:01,519 --> 00:02:04,239
I never should have left you behind.

36
00:02:08,159 --> 00:02:09,560
I'm so sorry.

37
00:02:13,879 --> 00:02:15,919
I'm so sorry, Nian.

38
00:02:20,599 --> 00:02:21,759
I'm sorry.

39
00:02:23,919 --> 00:02:26,960
(Three years ago)
If you hadn't run off with Zhenxuan,

40
00:02:27,360 --> 00:02:29,680
he wouldn't have died
of his illness out there.

41
00:02:30,319 --> 00:02:32,479
He could have had a bright future.

42
00:02:32,680 --> 00:02:33,479
It's you.

43
00:02:33,639 --> 00:02:37,080
Because of you, I never got
to see my son one last time.

44
00:02:37,199 --> 00:02:39,360
I've spent years looking for you.

45
00:02:40,879 --> 00:02:43,800
I wasn't hiding from you.

46
00:02:44,280 --> 00:02:46,120
Wenjun stopped us from seeing you.

47
00:02:47,199 --> 00:02:48,000
What?

48
00:02:48,599 --> 00:02:49,400
Wenjun?

49
00:02:49,520 --> 00:02:50,560
You didn't know?

50
00:02:53,360 --> 00:02:54,840
Zhenxuan was brilliant.

51
00:02:55,039 --> 00:02:56,479
Even after leaving the Qiao family,

52
00:02:56,479 --> 00:02:58,439
he could have made
a great life for himself.

53
00:03:00,120 --> 00:03:02,039
Too bad he had such
a backstabbing sister.

54
00:03:02,400 --> 00:03:03,560
She always went after him

55
00:03:03,560 --> 00:03:04,759
and sabotaged his business.

56
00:03:04,759 --> 00:03:06,080
He ended up drowning in debt.

57
00:03:07,599 --> 00:03:10,240
Debt collectors beat Zhenxuan up.

58
00:03:10,240 --> 00:03:11,680
We couldn't afford his medical bills.

59
00:03:13,960 --> 00:03:15,199
That's why he passed away.

60
00:03:17,039 --> 00:03:18,719
If you hadn't lured him away,

61
00:03:19,120 --> 00:03:21,199
none of this would have happened.

62
00:03:22,080 --> 00:03:22,879
So,

63
00:03:23,719 --> 00:03:25,479
I have to take Qiao Nian with me.

64
00:03:26,479 --> 00:03:28,599
What kind of life can you even give her?

65
00:03:29,039 --> 00:03:29,800
Do you want her

66
00:03:29,800 --> 00:03:31,879
to end up like Zhenxuan,
trapped in a gilded cage?

67
00:03:32,199 --> 00:03:34,080
Of course I'll give her the best.

68
00:03:34,725 --> 00:03:37,919
It'd be better than dragging her
through a life of poverty.

69
00:03:38,879 --> 00:03:41,960
Coming back to the Qiao family
is her best option.

70
00:03:42,680 --> 00:03:44,280
I know Qiao Wenjun too well.

71
00:03:45,039 --> 00:03:47,039
I won't let Nian walk into a trap.

72
00:03:47,400 --> 00:03:49,879
Don't worry. I'm here.

73
00:03:50,159 --> 00:03:51,719
No one will ever bully Qiao Nian.

74
00:03:51,719 --> 00:03:54,319
Fine. Then promise me something.

75
00:03:54,919 --> 00:03:56,039
Give me your word,

76
00:03:56,080 --> 00:03:57,719
so I can trust you with Nian.

77
00:04:00,199 --> 00:04:01,000
All right.

78
00:04:01,680 --> 00:04:03,240
Then let's make a deal.

79
00:04:04,800 --> 00:04:05,680
I promise.

80
00:04:06,000 --> 00:04:07,560
Once Qiao Nian grows up,

81
00:04:08,280 --> 00:04:11,199
I'll let her take over Qiao Group

82
00:04:12,080 --> 00:04:13,919
and make sure she has a bright future.

83
00:04:15,280 --> 00:04:18,639
But I never want Qiao Nian

84
00:04:20,120 --> 00:04:21,040
to see you again.

85
00:04:27,879 --> 00:04:28,759
(Nian,)

86
00:04:29,680 --> 00:04:32,319
(I have no choice but to leave you.)

87
00:04:34,079 --> 00:04:35,800
(Your grandpa will take care of you.)

88
00:04:37,759 --> 00:04:41,920
(Your dad left the Qiao family
to be free.)

89
00:04:43,120 --> 00:04:45,560
(But to secure your own freedom,)

90
00:04:46,279 --> 00:04:48,120
(I want you to return
to the Qiao family.)

91
00:04:51,360 --> 00:04:54,120
(Whether it becomes a cage
or a fortress depends on)

92
00:04:54,959 --> 00:04:57,680
(To Qiao Nian)
(whether you become its master.)

93
00:04:59,240 --> 00:05:00,079
(Nian,)

94
00:05:01,360 --> 00:05:02,560
(you've always been smart.)

95
00:05:03,519 --> 00:05:06,199
(I know you'll understand what I mean.)

96
00:05:09,680 --> 00:05:11,600
(By the time you read this letter,)

97
00:05:12,720 --> 00:05:15,600
(Mom will already be far away.)

98
00:05:19,199 --> 00:05:20,720
(When we meet again,)

99
00:05:21,160 --> 00:05:21,959
(maybe)

100
00:05:21,959 --> 00:05:24,560
(you'll have finished the path
your dad couldn't,)

101
00:05:26,360 --> 00:05:28,800
(and become the master
of your own fate.)

102
00:05:30,680 --> 00:05:31,920
(Take care of yourself.)

103
00:05:33,319 --> 00:05:34,839
(Love, Mom.)

104
00:05:50,639 --> 00:05:51,439
Yunyi,

105
00:05:52,000 --> 00:05:53,079
long time no see.

106
00:05:53,360 --> 00:05:54,240
Jiang Xiao?

107
00:06:00,879 --> 00:06:03,519
Do you like the room?

108
00:06:04,920 --> 00:06:05,720
Oh, right.

109
00:06:06,000 --> 00:06:07,800
I got you some art supplies too.

110
00:06:08,160 --> 00:06:10,240
I can't have our college star

111
00:06:10,439 --> 00:06:11,759
getting lonely in here.

112
00:06:14,560 --> 00:06:16,360
Thank you, Jiang Xiao.

113
00:06:16,839 --> 00:06:18,120
Sorry for the trouble.

114
00:06:18,399 --> 00:06:20,040
You don't need to thank me.

115
00:06:20,560 --> 00:06:22,040
We're old classmates.

116
00:06:22,360 --> 00:06:23,279
You can stay here

117
00:06:23,439 --> 00:06:24,519
as long as you want.

118
00:06:25,319 --> 00:06:26,240
Plus,

119
00:06:26,639 --> 00:06:28,439
I'll look after your daughter too.

120
00:06:29,439 --> 00:06:32,800
I'll have someone watching
over her every day.

121
00:06:33,959 --> 00:06:35,079
What do you mean?

122
00:06:39,040 --> 00:06:44,079
I mean I want you to stay here forever.

123
00:06:46,319 --> 00:06:47,839
Are you using Nian to threaten me?

124
00:06:47,839 --> 00:06:48,639
You!

125
00:06:52,079 --> 00:06:53,600
That's not what I meant.

126
00:06:55,040 --> 00:06:56,680
I just wanted you to know

127
00:06:57,959 --> 00:07:00,959
I've got my eye on her too.

128
00:07:03,680 --> 00:07:04,480
Come clean.

129
00:07:05,279 --> 00:07:07,199
Where did you hide Xie Yunyi?

130
00:07:08,720 --> 00:07:10,759
What did you do with Xie Yunyi?

131
00:07:19,600 --> 00:07:20,639
- Hello.
- Hello.

132
00:07:20,959 --> 00:07:25,079
Someone's downloaded our communication
and transaction records, Mr. Jiang.

133
00:07:25,600 --> 00:07:27,920
You won't be trying
to betray us, would you?

134
00:07:28,319 --> 00:07:28,959
What?

135
00:07:29,800 --> 00:07:33,879
That's impossible. I never left
this phone unattended.

136
00:07:39,800 --> 00:07:41,480
I know who it is.

137
00:07:48,240 --> 00:07:52,240
You had Xie Yunyi tamper with my phone.

138
00:07:52,920 --> 00:07:53,720
I did.

139
00:07:55,279 --> 00:07:55,680
I think

140
00:07:55,680 --> 00:07:57,920
you really want your brother
dead, don't you?

141
00:08:01,480 --> 00:08:04,279
My brother is already dead, isn't he?

142
00:08:04,560 --> 00:08:06,160
I ran a digital analysis.

143
00:08:06,439 --> 00:08:09,319
In your last video call
with your brother,

144
00:08:09,680 --> 00:08:12,839
his face and voice
were both AI-generated.

145
00:08:19,319 --> 00:08:20,680
My dear son,

146
00:08:22,319 --> 00:08:23,199
you've gotten smarter.

147
00:08:25,212 --> 00:08:27,092
Since you've figured it out,

148
00:08:27,439 --> 00:08:29,120
I won't hide it from you anymore.

149
00:08:29,680 --> 00:08:30,600
Your brother

150
00:08:31,000 --> 00:08:34,080
really did die abroad a few years ago.

151
00:08:34,440 --> 00:08:35,399
But

152
00:08:38,279 --> 00:08:41,720
I still have his ashes.

153
00:08:42,639 --> 00:08:45,919
You'll still do exactly as I say.

154
00:08:47,759 --> 00:08:48,919
Jiang Xiao,

155
00:08:50,039 --> 00:08:51,759
you're such a lowlife!

156
00:08:58,900 --> 00:09:04,870
♪So many words unsaid,
the deeper we fall, the more we fear♪

157
00:09:05,150 --> 00:09:12,750
♪Fate like a gamble,
locking us inside its game♪

158
00:09:12,800 --> 00:09:16,590
♪Hearts at play, truth and lies,
who could ever know♪

159
00:09:17,110 --> 00:09:20,390
♪Where this ends♪

160
00:09:20,390 --> 00:09:27,670
♪I try to walk away,
yet still step into the fire♪

161
00:09:27,670 --> 00:09:32,000
♪Your heartbeat pulls me under,
and I lose myself♪

162
00:09:32,040 --> 00:09:35,120
♪Love turns into pain♪

163
00:09:35,190 --> 00:09:39,310
♪Words betray us
until our eyes burn red♪

164
00:09:39,470 --> 00:09:42,950
♪Yet I still want you close♪

165
00:09:42,950 --> 00:09:47,120
♪Your tide breaks me,
and I fall for you again♪

166
00:09:47,120 --> 00:09:50,430
♪Even if love becomes nothing♪

167
00:09:50,430 --> 00:09:55,000
♪When love and hate fade
into the crowd and the ice melts♪

168
00:09:55,000 --> 00:10:01,310
♪Does it mean we could meet again?♪

169
